<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">首要目标：</span></strong><br />
<strong>GOI-116：安布罗斯餐厅</strong><br />
<strong>状态：</strong> <span style="color:green">●</span>活跃<span style="color:green">●</span><br />
