<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/ambrose-restaurant-hub/Bs0O0C1.png" width="150px" alt="Bs0O0C1.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
